body:
Are you running OVMS with the same config as in the example - https://github.com/openvinotoolkit/model_server/blob/develop/src/custom_nodes/image_transformation/config_with_preprocessing_node.json

Looking at the message you got it seems that your model is not configured to accept input in NHWC layout, which is a requirement for using binary inputs feature. 
https://github.com/openvinotoolkit/model_server/blob/develop/src/custom_nodes/image_transformation/config_with_preprocessing_node.json#L7

Make sure you set `layout` parameter in your model configuration to `NHWC`.

Yes, I used the configuration of the example, I did not set the default configuration.
The option 1 run success.
`libcustom_node_image_transformation.so` made by `make BASE_OS=centos`.
Could you run model server in debug mode (use `--log_level DEBUG` with the command you launch model server with) and post logs here?

I ran it again, this is the log.
